<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Locale: I need to get translationData in specified encoding e.g. WIN1251 (one-byte Cyrillic encoding) instead UTF-8.</p>

<p>Now I have to override getTranslationData method and realize converted via iconv function, but I think It is not a right way in general.</p>

